title: [The Wage and Dagger, Eatery]
description: Thick indigo velvet curtains have been opened to admit light from street lanterns and the moons, allowing diners to actually see what they are eating, which may be a mistake considering the neglected surroundings.  Although some of the food aromas are enticing, the wafting scent of mildew threatens to spoil the appetite.  Serving wenches move quietly between the tables, balancing stacks of plates along both arms.
